name: deeplabcut
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.2.1" %}

package:
  name: deeplabcut
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/d/deeplabcut/deeplabcut-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c02473287db26b0fb9006338f25af858a441b16fae6c52d9a32496d719375489
  patches:
    - relax_requirements.patch
    - silence_light_mode_warning.patch
    - do_not_force_tf_v1.patch

build:
  number: 1
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --no-deps
  # Confirm with upstream before making this entry point
  # https://github.com/DeepLabCut/DeepLabCut/pull/1547
  entry_points:
    - dlc = deeplabcut.cli:main
    - deeplabcut = deeplabcut:launch_dlc

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - filterpy >=1.4.4
    - ruamel.yaml >=0.15.0
    - imgaug >=0.4.0
    - numba >=0.54
    - matplotlib-base >=3.3
    - networkx >=2.6
    - numpy >=1.18.5
    - opencv
    - pandas >=1.0.1
    - scikit-image >=0.17,!=0.18.2
    - scikit-learn >=1.0
    - scipy >=1.4
    - statsmodels >=0.11,!=0.13.2
    - pytables >=3.7
    - tensorflow >=2.0
    - tensorpack >=0.11
    - tf_slim >=1.1.0
    - tqdm
    - pyyaml
    - pillow >=7.1
